parts.prose:
- Enable account-level S3 block public access: aws s3control put-public-access-block --account-id <id> --public-access-block-configuration BlockPublicAcls=true,IgnorePublicAcls=true,BlockPublicPolicy=true,RestrictPublicBuckets=true
- Audit public buckets: aws s3api list-buckets | jq -r '.Buckets[].Name' | xargs -I{} aws s3api get-public-access-block --bucket {}
- Review CloudFront distributions: aws cloudfront list-distributions
